---
title: Quick Pork Spaghetti Bolognese with Veggies & Grated Parmesan
description: It’s spag bol’ night, get excited, especially because we’re swapping out beef for pork mince and cooking it up in an Aussie spice
mix and Worcestershire sauce (don’t worry we have no clue how to say it either). Everyone will be loving this new take on a
classic.
